ygData.messageBody:
Hi everyone:) Well I'm probably going to go back to playing my
Rogue, Garret. I've enjoyed the Enchanter but (class imbalance
aside) I just love the Rogue more. And fun is the most important
part...Anyway the two chars I have on Brell are:

Garret, 7th Wood Elf Rogue
Timarius, 5th High Elf Enchanter

I also have several other characters other places but those are the
ones I am focusing for sake of interest in the Guild. Look me up
sometime:)

*hugs*
Lonewolf
